rules.description: Go to tab to left (right_shift+u to cmd+shift+[)
Go to tab to right (right_shift+o to cmd+shift+])
wrap with " (left_shift+right_shift+2 to clipboard wrapped with ")
wrap with () (left_shift+right_shift+9 to clipboard wrapped with ())
wrap with ` (left_shift+right_shift+` to clipboard wrapped with `)
